OL,3,CImplications of Edwards scandal for
OL,4,CBBC archive
OL,6,GThe disgrace of Huw Edwards poses many
OL,7,Ghuge challenges for the BBC.
OL,9,FThese are issues for the corporation
OL,10,Fitself and society as a whole which
OL,11,Fwill be widely discussed elsewhere.
OL,13,FBut it also poses huge challenges
OL,14,Fconcerning the use of archive material.
OL,16,FAccording to reports over the weekend,
OL,17,Fthe BBC is "deleting" material from
OL,18,Fits archive.
