OL,6,FGenerally I do not like re-editing
OL,7,Fmaterial because things which were
OL,8,Facceptable at the time it was made are
OL,9,Fno longer deemed appropriate.
OL,11,FI quite understand why the name of Guy
OL,12,FGibson's dog in The Dambusters causes
OL,13,Fhurt and offence but I also believe
OL,14,Fmost people are intelligent enough to
OL,15,Funderstand the context.
OL,17,FBut removing a cameo appearance by a
OL,18,Fdisgraced figure from a programme
OL,19,Fwhich could otherwise still be enjoyed
OL,20,Fis a different matter.
