OL,6,FOn balance, I think we have to accept
OL,7,Fthat it will be impossible to use any
OL,8,Ffootage of BBC coverage which includes
OL,9,FEdwards' face or voice.
OL,11,FIt distorts the story by doing this.
OL,12,FFar more people, for instance, heard
OL,13,FEdwards announce the Queen's death
OL,14,Fthan heard his counterparts on other
OL,15,Fchannels.
OL,17,FBut the sad truth is that any clip
OL,18,Fwith Edwards at the helm would now
OL,19,Fdistract from the story and cause
OL,20,Fupset to some.
