OL,6,FThe choice would therefore be between
OL,7,Fusing other parts of the BBC's
OL,8,Fcoverage or ` say ` using material
OL,9,Ffrom another channel.
OL,11,FI would not approve of any doctoring
OL,12,Fof BBC material to use another voice
OL,13,For presenter ` that is unethical and
OL,14,Fas bad as it's destruction.
OL,16,FThe thoughts of any decent person at
OL,17,Fthis time must be with innocent
OL,18,Fchildren. Internet crime is not
OL,19,Fvictimless.
